/2147530/extras/1dfa7fcb9204934f5a2aa956f840faeb.poster.avif?t=1753897492\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/1dfa7fcb9204934f5a2aa956f840faeb.webm?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/1dfa7fcb9204934f5a2aa956f840faeb.mp4?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/e61cc8578986755d522dfcfdd29863ee.avif?t=1753897492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras_big/e61cc8578986755d522dfcfdd29863ee.avif?t=1753897492 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take down the Lords of Hell, fallen angels, and the guardians of Heaven in brutal encounters that will push your power to its absolute limits. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/3bd2f700117639ea0e8cc44ac6ace276.poster.avif?t=1753897492\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/3bd2f700117639ea0e8cc44ac6ace276.webm?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/3bd2f700117639ea0e8cc44ac6ace276.mp4?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/6965e4f597164e3f50c71b4eeb289427.avif?t=1753897492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras_big/6965e4f597164e3f50c71b4eeb289427.avif?t=1753897492 width=800 height=124 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harness the power of the elements in chaotic battles where each one plays a vital role. The system follows a rock-paper-scissors logic — Water extinguishes Fire, Fire explodes Gas, and Electricity becomes deadly in moist environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/143bd32ed06163627937a117dec8cef3.poster.avif?t=1753897492\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/143bd32ed06163627937a117dec8cef3.webm?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/143bd32ed06163627937a117dec8cef3.mp4?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Devastating Effects</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elemental attacks inflict brutal conditions like freezing, burning, bleeding, and shocking, drastically altering the pace of combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/a46894a111f5a92bbcb82e29561516f5.poster.avif?t=1753897492\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/a46894a111f5a92bbcb82e29561516f5.webm?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/a46894a111f5a92bbcb82e29561516f5.mp4?t=1753897492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Elemental Interactions & Adaptive Enemies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elements react with one another in powerful and unexpected ways — fire ignites, water douses, electricity surges through moisture, and more. These interactions can drastically alter the flow of battle. Meanwhile, enemies adapt to their current state, gaining new resistances and vulnerabilities on the fly. To dominate the battlefield, you'll need to read the situation, combine elements wisely, and strike where it hurts most.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras/6b873ab56306a4f6b52934a118c5c6e5.avif?t=1753897492\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147530/extras_big/6b873ab56306a4f6b52934a118c5c6e5.avif?t=1753897492 width=800 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
